# Large model / data files — contents of data/ and models/ are fetched
# from Zenodo at install time, not committed. README.md + checksum files
# in those dirs ARE committed.
*.pt
*.bin
*.safetensors
*.h5
*.hdf5
*.npy
*.npz
*.parquet
data/**
!data/README.md
!data/checksums.sha256
models/**
!models/README.md
!models/checksums.sha256

# Container artifacts (built locally, not committed)
*.sif
*.tar
*.tar.gz

# Secrets / credentials
.env
*.pem

# Claude Code instructions (not for public release)
CLAUDE.md
